tags.name: Bubolz Park
tags.note: At this park, baseball takes center stage with many t-ball, baseball, and softball games and practices held here. Playground equipment, an open shelter, concession stand, and indoor bathrooms surround the ball diamond.

tags.name: American Legion Gosz-Novak Post 199 Memorial Park
tags.note: This park is a prized memorial to those who have served in our area. Featuring a T-33A United States Air Force military aircraft that has been on loan since 1967 from the National Museum of United States Air Force
